        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Elaine M. Checketts Military Families Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to amend regulations to provide that approved parental leave shall not terminate upon the death of the child for whom the leave is taken.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
